Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.58,0:00:13.86,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我现在在哪?\N{\fnArial\fs48}Where am I now?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.68,0:00:19.16,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}爸爸?\N{\fnArial\fs48}Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.64,0:00:21.12,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}史蒂文?\N{\fnArial\fs48}Huh? Steven?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.58,0:00:22.78,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}爸爸,是你!\N{\fnArial\fs48}Dad, it's you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.78,0:00:25.14,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}史蒂文!我的小子!\N{\fnArial\fs48}Steven! My little man!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.46,0:00:26.24,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}爸爸!\N{\fnArial\fs48}Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.26,0:00:28.98,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}当蓝钻石抓走你时,我担心死了\N{\fnArial\fs48}When Blue Diamond took you, I got so scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.98,0:00:30.34,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}然后宝石人们说你可能\N{\fnArial\fs48}And then the Gems said you might be in
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.36,0:00:33.22,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}在那种非常恐怖的人类动物园里,被锁链束缚在墙边\N{\fnArial\fs48}some horrible human zoo all chained up to a wall
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.22,0:00:35.90,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}为了为了点花生而出丑\N{\fnArial\fs48}doing tricks for peanuts.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.25,0:00:38.64,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}嘿,嘿,没什么,崽子\N{\fnArial\fs48}Hey, hey, it's okay, schtu-ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.64,0:00:40.50,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}你的老爸好得很\N{\fnArial\fs48}Your old man's perfectly fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.94,0:00:43.28,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}等等,你们是怎么来到这的?\N{\fnArial\fs48}Wait, how'd you even get out here?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.54,0:00:45.06,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我们在地球上有艘宝石人的太空飞船\N{\fnArial\fs48}We got on a Gem ship from Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.32,0:00:46.94,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我会在回家的路上详细跟你说\N{\fnArial\fs48}I'll tell you about it on the way home.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.98,0:00:48.56,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我和宝石人们分开了\N{\fnArial\fs48}I got separated from the Gems.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.56,0:00:50.46,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我们得找到她们并救你出去\N{\fnArial\fs48}We got to find them and bust you out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.98,0:00:53.78,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}其实,从那里是出不去的\N{\fnArial\fs48}Well, you're not gonna get out that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.96,0:00:55.07,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我已经试过了\N{\fnArial\fs48}I've already tried.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.09,0:00:55.73,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}什么?\N{\fnArial\fs48}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.67,0:00:58.94,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}那么,如果我们去找的话总会有条路的\N{\fnArial\fs48}Well, there might be another way out if we can find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.94,0:00:59.80,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}嘎雷格!\N{\fnArial\fs48}Ga-reg!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.98,0:01:03.44,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}跟你在一起的是谁?\N{\fnArial\fs48}Who is that with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.82,0:01:05.44,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}他是新朋友吗,嘎雷格?\N{\fnArial\fs48}Is this a new friend, Ga-reg?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.76,0:01:08.18,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}Y6,J10,他是-\N{\fnArial\fs48}Wy-Six, Jay-Ten, this is --
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.18,0:01:10.04,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}老爸是我的!\N{\fnArial\fs48}Let me have my dad back already!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.31,0:01:13.02,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}嘿,别这样,放松点\N{\fnArial\fs48}Hey, don't be like that. Relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.31,0:01:16.36,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}这些人在我来之后对我一直非常好\N{\fnArial\fs48}These people have treated me so well since I got here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.82,0:01:17.29,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}什么?\N{\fnArial\fs48}Wha?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.00,0:01:19.42,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}你好,你好\N{\fnArial\fs48}Greetings, greetings.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.44,0:01:20.93,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}你好,嘎雷格\N{\fnArial\fs48}-Wow. -Hello, Ga-reg.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.96,0:01:23.29,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}喔,一个新的小朋友-嘎雷格\N{\fnArial\fs48}-Wow, a new small friend. -Ga-reg.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.51,0:01:25.27,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}大家听着,这是史蒂文\N{\fnArial\fs48}Everyone, this is Steven.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.49,0:01:26.60,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}他是我儿子\N{\fnArial\fs48}He's my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.11,0:01:29.11,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}呃,嗨\N{\fnArial\fs48}Uh, hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.42,0:01:30.80,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}嗨\N{\fnArial\fs48}Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.09,0:01:33.64,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}谢谢你们给我爸爸梳辫子\N{\fnArial\fs48}Thanks for braiding my dad's hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.96,0:01:36.76,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}史蒂文,这些人是那些\N{\fnArial\fs48}Steven, these people are the descendants of humans
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.76,0:01:39.27,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}几千年前被宝石人带来的人类的后代\N{\fnArial\fs48}brought here by Gems thousands of years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.53,0:01:41.53,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}他们从没见过地球\N{\fnArial\fs48}They've never seen the Earth before.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.53,0:01:42.85,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}这听起来很疯狂吧?\N{\fnArial\fs48}Isn't that wild?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.20,0:01:46.04,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}史蒂梵,嘎雷格讲过你的故事\N{\fnArial\fs48}Ste-van, Ga-reg has told stories of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.40,0:01:47.91,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}"薯条渣,薯条渣!"\N{\fnArial\fs48}"The bits, the bits!"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.09,0:01:48.92,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}那是你,对吧?\N{\fnArial\fs48}That's you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.27,0:01:53.11,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}薯条渣,薯条渣,薯条渣!\N{\fnArial\fs48}The bits, the bits, the bits!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.40,0:01:54.59,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}来啊,一起喊啊\N{\fnArial\fs48}Come on, say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.24,0:01:55.93,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}咱们走吧\N{\fnArial\fs48}Let's get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.20,0:01:58.38,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我们之前见到了一扇连接着动物园的门\N{\fnArial\fs48}We came across a door that leads into the zoo,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.56,0:02:00.38,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}但是我们从外面打不开\N{\fnArial\fs48}but we couldn't open it from the other side.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.73,0:02:02.91,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}让我们找到并试着开启它吧\N{\fnArial\fs48}Let's find it and try to open it from in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.20,0:02:04.76,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}一扇门?真的?\N{\fnArial\fs48}A door? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.13,0:02:07.24,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}好吧,咱们今晚找找看\N{\fnArial\fs48}All right. Let's find it tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.56,0:02:10.04,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}这会容易一些,如果是在"日常"后的话\N{\fnArial\fs48}It'll be easier to look for it after the routine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.40,0:02:12.91,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}大家好\N{\fnArial\fs48}{\i1}Greeting, everyone.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.11,0:02:15.67,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}是时候开始"日常任务"了\N{\fnArial\fs48}{\i1}It's time to start{\i} {\i1}the daily routine.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.07,0:02:19.84,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}请在指定的用餐时间享用你的大餐!\N{\fnArial\fs48}{\i1}Please enjoy your meal during{\i} {\i1}this designated eating period.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.09,0:02:21.04,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}那是谁?\N{\fnArial\fs48}Who was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.19,0:02:23.93,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}史蒂梵不知道微语音是什么\N{\fnArial\fs48}Ste-van does not know what a little voice is.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.93,0:02:26.60,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}就像嘎雷格刚来时一样\N{\fnArial\fs48}Just like Ga-reg when he first arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.42,0:02:30.84,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我们的微语音指引我们在这里的生活\N{\fnArial\fs48}Our little voices guide us through life here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.33,0:02:33.13,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}你们现在肯定都饿了\N{\fnArial\fs48}{\i1}You all must be hungry now.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.13,0:02:34.58,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}-是的-我们都是\N{\fnArial\fs48}-Yes, yes. -We are.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.56,0:02:37.47,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}呃,爸爸?\N{\fnArial\fs48}Um, Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.47,0:02:39.80,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}别担心,史蒂文,我们会离开这里的\N{\fnArial\fs48}Don't worry, Steven. We'll get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.98,0:02:42.29,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}但现在,让我们先融入这里\N{\fnArial\fs48}But for now, let's just play along.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.00,0:02:47.08,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}给你,嘎雷格\N{\fnArial\fs48}Here you go, Ga-reg.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.40,0:02:48.45,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}哦,谢谢\N{\fnArial\fs48}Oh, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.76,0:02:51.40,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}史蒂梵,今天的水果是紫色的\N{\fnArial\fs48}Ste-van, today the fruit is purple.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.00,0:02:53.80,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}你们喜欢食物吗?\N{\fnArial\fs48}{\i1}Are you enjoying the food?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.89,0:02:55.18,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}噢,是的\N{\fnArial\fs48}Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.18,0:02:57.36,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}食物怎么样?好吃吗?\N{\fnArial\fs48}{\i1}How is the food?{\i} {\i1}Is it good?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.36,0:02:59.73,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}当然,非常美味\N{\fnArial\fs48}Yes. It is delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.82,0:03:04.36,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}现在该玩耍了\N{\fnArial\fs48}{\i1}Now it's time to play.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.42,0:03:14.07,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}现在,每个人,将手伸出,就像你能\N{\fnArial\fs48}{\i1}Now, everyone,{\i} {\i1}reach up like you're going{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.07,0:03:15.58,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}触碰到太空\N{\fnArial\fs48}{\i1}to touch outer space.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.87,0:03:16.47,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}就是这样\N{\fnArial\fs48}{\i1}That's it.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.93,0:03:17.87,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}伸的高些\N{\fnArial\fs48}{\i1}Reach up high.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.47,0:03:19.71,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}这很有趣吧?\N{\fnArial\fs48}{\i1}Wasn't that fun?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.98,0:03:22.98,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}从昨天到现在我还没这么开心过\N{\fnArial\fs48}I have not had that much fun since yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.87,0:03:26.60,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}现在该停下闻一闻花朵了\N{\fnArial\fs48}{\i1}It's time to stop{\i} {\i1}and smell the flowers.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.62,0:03:30.47,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}如果我不想闻花朵呢?\N{\fnArial\fs48}What if I don't want to smell the flowers?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.71,0:03:32.36,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}你为什么不想这么做呢?\N{\fnArial\fs48}Why wouldn't you want to do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.38,0:03:39.20,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}该洗漱了,所有人\N{\fnArial\fs48}{\i1}Time to clean up, everyone.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.49,0:03:41.96,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}让我们洗个清爽的澡吧\N{\fnArial\fs48}{\i1}Let's all take{\i} {\i1}a refreshing bath.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.60,0:03:50.40,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}看我的水花,嘎雷格!\N{\fnArial\fs48}Watch my splash, Ga-reg!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.40,0:03:55.31,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}不错!\N{\fnArial\fs48}Nice one!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.80,0:03:57.84,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}嘎雷格,看我的!\N{\fnArial\fs48}Ga-reg, watch mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.00,0:04:02.60,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}那是我见过的最小的水花\N{\fnArial\fs48}Those are the tiniest splashes I've ever seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.78,0:04:03.71,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}看这个\N{\fnArial\fs48}Watch this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.18,0:04:08.06,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}嘿,Y6,你听说过入水炮弹吗?\N{\fnArial\fs48}Hey, Wy-Six, - you ever heard of a cannonball?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.96,0:04:10.00,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}从来没听过\N{\fnArial\fs48}I've never heard it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.20,0:04:11.33,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}跟我说说呗\N{\fnArial\fs48}Tell me what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.33,0:04:12.46,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}看这个\N{\fnArial\fs48}Check this out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.71,0:04:13.93,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我会表演给你看\N{\fnArial\fs48}I'll show you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.44,0:04:15.82,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}入水炮弹!\N{\fnArial\fs48}Cannonball!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.84,0:04:21.27,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}-入水炮弹!-入水炮弹!\N{\fnArial\fs48}-Cannonball! -Cannonball!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.69,0:04:23.98,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}你们很喜欢在泳池中清洁自己吧?\N{\fnArial\fs48}{\i1}Wouldn't you like{\i} {\i1}to clean off in the pool?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.98,0:04:26.00,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}好吧\N{\fnArial\fs48}All right, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.44,0:04:28.98,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}入水炮弹!\N{\fnArial\fs48}Yeah! Cannonball!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.44,0:04:31.05,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}嘿,你还好吗?\N{\fnArial\fs48}Hey, you hanging in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.53,0:04:34.07,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我没法理解,他们都那么开心\N{\fnArial\fs48}I can't believe this. They're all so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.42,0:04:37.18,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}就好像他们不知道自己被困在这里一样\N{\fnArial\fs48}It's like they don't even know that they're trapped here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.58,0:04:38.84,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}其实,他们当然不知道\N{\fnArial\fs48}Well, of course they don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.00,0:04:40.76,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}他们没去过其他地方\N{\fnArial\fs48}They've never been anywhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.07,0:04:43.53,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}他们喜欢在这里,我是指,你看看这个地方\N{\fnArial\fs48}They love it here. - I mean, look at this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.53,0:04:44.53,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}你能怪他们吗?\N{\fnArial\fs48}Can you blame them?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.53,0:04:45.98,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}他们有所需的一切\N{\fnArial\fs48}They've got everything they need,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.98,0:04:47.84,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}而且不需要为任何事担心\N{\fnArial\fs48}and they never have to worry about a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.78,0:04:49.73,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我觉得你是对的\N{\fnArial\fs48}I guess you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.87,0:04:52.00,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}\N{\fnArial\fs48}Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.33,0:04:58.28,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}现在该"晚安"了\N{\fnArial\fs48}{\i1}And now it's time{\i} {\i1}to say good night.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.58,0:05:00.74,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}晚安,各位\N{\fnArial\fs48}{\i1}Good night, everyone.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.75,0:05:02.35,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}睡个好觉\N{\fnArial\fs48}{\i1}Sweet dreams.{\i} -
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.62,0:05:05.82,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}天哪,划了一天水居然还累了\N{\fnArial\fs48}Geez, I sure am tired from doing a whole lot of nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.27,0:05:07.87,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}那么,晚安,崽子\N{\fnArial\fs48}Well, good night, schtu-ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.58,0:05:12.78,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}爸爸,现在是我们逃出去的时候\N{\fnArial\fs48}Dad. Now's our chance to get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.11,0:05:16.93,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}天,微语音真的让我\N{\fnArial\fs48}Man, little voice has really got me
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.93,0:05:18.76,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}接受了动物园人的作息时间了\N{\fnArial\fs48}on that zooman sleep schedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.69,0:05:20.29,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}哦\N{\fnArial\fs48}Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.56,0:05:22.31,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}这是...\N{\fnArial\fs48}Is that...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.16,0:05:24.40,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}这是大门\N{\fnArial\fs48}It's the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.64,0:05:26.60,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}好,那么我们该怎么打开它呢?\N{\fnArial\fs48}Great. How do we get it open?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.76,0:05:32.39,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}嘎雷格!\N{\fnArial\fs48}Ga-reg!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.39,0:05:33.02,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}哦!\N{\fnArial\fs48}Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.02,0:05:33.76,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}史蒂梵!\N{\fnArial\fs48}Ste-van!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.78,0:05:34.13,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}蛤?\N{\fnArial\fs48}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.42,0:05:36.76,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}原来是你们制造的噪音\N{\fnArial\fs48}So you're the ones making the noise.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.76,0:05:38.00,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}你们在做什么?\N{\fnArial\fs48}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.33,0:05:38.92,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}这是个游戏吗?\N{\fnArial\fs48}Is it a game?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.27,0:05:40.31,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我们能一起玩吗?\N{\fnArial\fs48}Can we play, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.71,0:05:41.87,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}这不是游戏\N{\fnArial\fs48}It's not a game.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.18,0:05:43.44,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我们得想方法让门打开\N{\fnArial\fs48}We need to get this door open.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.02,0:05:45.47,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}"门"是什么?\N{\fnArial\fs48}What is a door?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.84,0:05:48.44,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}就是,墙的一部分,但能开\N{\fnArial\fs48}Like, this part of the wall but open.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.64,0:05:50.89,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}墙不会开\N{\fnArial\fs48}Walls don't open.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.20,0:05:52.44,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}墙就是墙\N{\fnArial\fs48}They're walls.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.78,0:05:55.07,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}有个关于会开的墙的故事\N{\fnArial\fs48}There is a story of an opening wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.47,0:05:59.09,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}很久以前,一个宝石人从墙洞走进来\N{\fnArial\fs48}A very long time a go, a Gem came through a wall hole
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.09,0:06:01.54,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}帮助一个受伤的人\N{\fnArial\fs48}to help someone who was hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.98,0:06:03.98,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}你说的"受伤"指什么?\N{\fnArial\fs48}What do you mean hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.27,0:06:07.18,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我不知道,我不知道什么叫"受伤"\N{\fnArial\fs48}I don't know. I don't know what hurt is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.64,0:06:08.73,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我知道"受伤"!\N{\fnArial\fs48}I know what hurt is!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.18,0:06:09.98,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}你知道?\N{\fnArial\fs48}You do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.71,0:06:13.82,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}呃,就像你感觉很难受\N{\fnArial\fs48}Um, it's like when you feel bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.18,0:06:14.98,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}难受?\N{\fnArial\fs48}Bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.31,0:06:16.98,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}对,就像,好的对立面\N{\fnArial\fs48}Yes, like, the opposite of good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.71,0:06:19.62,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}如果那是唯一的方法,那么,爸爸\N{\fnArial\fs48}If that's the only way out, then, Dad,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.87,0:06:21.36,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}狠狠的打我脸吧\N{\fnArial\fs48}slug me in the face.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.62,0:06:23.86,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}什么?!我才不会打你呢!\N{\fnArial\fs48}What?! I'm not gonna hit you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.18,0:06:25.73,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}这是我们的出路\N{\fnArial\fs48}It's our ticket out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.73,0:06:27.24,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我们中的一个得受伤\N{\fnArial\fs48}One of us has to get hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.51,0:06:30.13,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}好吧,那么,你打我吧\N{\fnArial\fs48}Okay, well, then{\i1} you{\i} hit{\i1} me.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.40,0:06:31.03,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}你确定?\N{\fnArial\fs48}You sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.40,0:06:33.87,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}当然,我愿意为团队挨揍\N{\fnArial\fs48}Yeah. I'll take one for the team.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.51,0:06:41.42,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}来吧,让我看看你怎么样\N{\fnArial\fs48}Come on, give me all you got.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.42,0:06:42.58,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我能承受的\N{\fnArial\fs48}I can take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.52,0:06:48.98,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}入水炮弹!\N{\fnArial\fs48}Cannonball!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.04,0:06:51.76,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}呃,怎么样?\N{\fnArial\fs48}Uh, how was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.07,0:06:52.96,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}可以\N{\fnArial\fs48}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.96,0:06:54.04,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}有人来吗?\N{\fnArial\fs48}Anyone coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.84,0:06:55.83,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}看起来不像\N{\fnArial\fs48}Doesn't look like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.47,0:06:58.29,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我该再试一次吗?\N{\fnArial\fs48}Should I try it again?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.58,0:07:01.13,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}如果再来一次,就没什么需要解救了\N{\fnArial\fs48}There won't be anything left to rescue if you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.69,0:07:02.93,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我们现在该怎么办?\N{\fnArial\fs48}What do we do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.64,0:07:06.14,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}看她说什么了\N{\fnArial\fs48}Whatever she says.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.49,0:07:08.73,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}现在是"天选"的时候了\N{\fnArial\fs48}{\i1}It is time{\i} {\i1}for the choosening.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.04,0:07:11.91,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}请在"天选"的圈子处集合\N{\fnArial\fs48}{\i1}Please gather around{\i} {\i1}the circle of choosening.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.33,0:07:15.60,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}史蒂梵,嘎雷格,"天选"马上就要开始了\N{\fnArial\fs48}Ste-van, Ga-reg, the choosening will start soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.62,0:07:18.04,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}跟我们去吧,总算-总算要来了!\N{\fnArial\fs48}Come with us. It's -- it's finally time!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.87,0:07:24.11,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}嘎雷格,跟我们一起走到圈子里\N{\fnArial\fs48}Ga-reg, step into the circle with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.40,0:07:25.62,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}这是某人的生日吗?\N{\fnArial\fs48}Is it somebody's birthday?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.62,0:07:28.51,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}史蒂梵,在这里等着,直到"天选"结束\N{\fnArial\fs48}Ste-van, wait here until the choosening is complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.98,0:07:33.42,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}"天选"对我们是非常特别的活动\N{\fnArial\fs48}The choosening is a very special event to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.73,0:07:36.53,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我们很高兴在这么好的时刻你能来\N{\fnArial\fs48}We're glad to have you with us at such a wonderful time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.93,0:07:38.02,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}很高兴来这里\N{\fnArial\fs48}Glad to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.02,0:07:40.09,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}让"天选"开始吧\N{\fnArial\fs48}{\i1}Let the choosening begin.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.18,0:07:48.21,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}U12,请站到圈子的中央\N{\fnArial\fs48}{\i1}U12, please step into{\i} {\i1}the center of the circle.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.09,0:07:51.29,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}F3...哈?\N{\fnArial\fs48}{\i1}-F3...{\i} -Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.31,0:07:54.27,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}请站到圈子中央\N{\fnArial\fs48}{\i1}...please step into{\i} {\i1}the center of the circle.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.60,0:07:57.09,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}你们已经被"天选"为一对了\N{\fnArial\fs48}{\i1}You have been choosened{\i} {\i1}for each other.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.44,0:07:58.56,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}等等\N{\fnArial\fs48}Wait a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.87,0:08:01.96,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}这不是强行配对吗?\N{\fnArial\fs48}Is this some kind of matchmaking thing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.89,0:08:05.49,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}这类乌托邦总有漏洞\N{\fnArial\fs48}There's always a catch to these utopias.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.87,0:08:09.84,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}嘎雷格,不管是谁被"天选"给你,都非常幸运\N{\fnArial\fs48}Ga-reg, whoever is choosen for you will be very lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.18,0:08:14.20,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}J10,请站到圈子中央\N{\fnArial\fs48}{\i1}Jay-Ten, please step into{\i} {\i1}the center of the circle.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.29,0:08:14.16,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63\pos(960,120)}哦,天哪\N{\fnArial\fs48}Oh, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.44,0:08:17.53,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}史蒂文,帮帮我\N{\fnArial\fs48}Steven, help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.53,0:08:18.54,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}别担心,爸爸\N{\fnArial\fs48}Don't worry, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.93,0:08:21.54,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}你是新来的,也许你不会被"天选"\N{\fnArial\fs48}You're new here, so maybe you won't get choosened.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.82,0:08:22.24,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}对啊\N{\fnArial\fs48}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.56,0:08:23.56,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}嘎雷格\N{\fnArial\fs48}Ga-reg.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.93,0:08:26.44,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}请站到圈子中央\N{\fnArial\fs48}{\i1}Please step into{\i} {\i1}the center of the circle.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.44,0:08:29.02,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}等等,也许这是个意外\N{\fnArial\fs48}Hold on, maybe there's been a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.02,0:08:31.59,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}嘎雷格,J10在等你啊\N{\fnArial\fs48}Ga-reg, Jay-Ten is waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.82,0:08:36.24,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我能看出来发生什么了\N{\fnArial\fs48}I see what is going on here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.47,0:08:37.06,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}你确定?\N{\fnArial\fs48}You do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.51,0:08:38.56,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}你只是害羞啦!\N{\fnArial\fs48}You are just shy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.84,0:08:39.48,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}呃?\N{\fnArial\fs48}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.71,0:08:40.98,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}别担心\N{\fnArial\fs48}Do not worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.89,0:08:45.94,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}现在请接触对方的手\N{\fnArial\fs48}Now touch hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.94,0:08:48.71,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}等等!在地球上不是这样的!\N{\fnArial\fs48}Hold on! This isn't how it works on Earth!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.22,0:08:53.49,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我不想被告知我和谁是"天选"的\N{\fnArial\fs48}I don't want to be told who to be choosened with.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.89,0:08:56.09,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}嘎雷格,这毫无道理\N{\fnArial\fs48}Ga-reg, this makes no sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.24,0:08:58.11,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}为什么你不想被"天选"?\N{\fnArial\fs48}Why wouldn't you want to be choosened?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.53,0:09:00.98,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}你看,在地球上,就没有语音\N{\fnArial\fs48}Look, back on Earth, there was no voice
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.98,0:09:02.49,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}告诉你该跟谁在一起\N{\fnArial\fs48}to tell you who to be with.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.51,0:09:04.12,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}这是你自己的选择\N{\fnArial\fs48}It was your own decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.60,0:09:06.22,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我母亲和父亲走到一起\N{\fnArial\fs48}My mom and dad didn't get together
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.22,0:09:08.04,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}并不是因为有人告诉他们如此\N{\fnArial\fs48}because someone told them to.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.51,0:09:11.91,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}他们花时间了解对方并坠入爱河\N{\fnArial\fs48}They spent time getting to know one another and fell in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.20,0:09:15.38,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}他们"天选"了对方,因为这是他们自己的选择\N{\fnArial\fs48}They choosened each other 'cause that's what they choosed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.89,0:09:17.30,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}嗯,我知道了\N{\fnArial\fs48}Hmm, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.71,0:09:19.64,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}如果在地球上是这样,那么...\N{\fnArial\fs48}If that's how it's done on Earth, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.67,0:09:21.97,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我选择嘎雷格\N{\fnArial\fs48}I choose Ga-reg.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.97,0:09:23.94,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我也选择嘎雷格!\N{\fnArial\fs48}And I also choose Ga-reg.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.13,0:09:26.98,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}等等!\N{\fnArial\fs48}Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.62,0:09:29.44,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我也得说句话\N{\fnArial\fs48}I get a say in this, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.80,0:09:32.98,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}你们都非常好,而且我很荣幸,而且是的\N{\fnArial\fs48}You're all very nice, and I'm flattered, and yes,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.00,0:09:35.00,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}你们可以选择任何想要的人,\N{\fnArial\fs48}you get to choose whoever you want,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.00,0:09:39.60,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}但我也得说我选择\N{\fnArial\fs48}but I also get to say that I choose
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.96,0:09:42.04,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}呃...不是你们中的任何一个\N{\fnArial\fs48}um...none of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.82,0:09:51.03,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}喔!嘿,别哭啊\N{\fnArial\fs48}Whoa! Hey, don't cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.40,0:09:53.14,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}你们可以选择其他人\N{\fnArial\fs48}You can choose someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.36,0:09:56.18,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我感觉不好\N{\fnArial\fs48}I feel not good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.82,0:09:58.67,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我感觉很糟\N{\fnArial\fs48}I feel bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.67,0:10:02.20,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}这就是-就是受伤吗?\N{\fnArial\fs48}Could this be -- is this hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.69,0:10:04.96,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}为什么嘎雷格要伤害我们?\N{\fnArial\fs48}Why would Ga-reg hurt us?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.56,0:10:07.45,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}将伤害带走吧\N{\fnArial\fs48}Take this hurt away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.71,0:10:10.58,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我"天选"带着我爸逃跑\N{\fnArial\fs48}I choosen to take my dad and run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.11,0:10:15.98,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}看着点那个-呕!\N{\fnArial\fs48}Watch out for that -- oof!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.56,0:10:23.71,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我从还有所有头发开始就没伤过这么多人的心\N{\fnArial\fs48}I haven't broken this many hearts since I had all my hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.18,0:10:28.60,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}嘿,快回来\N{\fnArial\fs48}Hey, get back here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.00,0:10:30.14,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}这真是疯了\N{\fnArial\fs48}This is nuts.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.91,0:10:34.49,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}赶快下来吧!\N{\fnArial\fs48}Just come down!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.49,0:10:35.71,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}让我们谈谈\N{\fnArial\fs48}Let's talk about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.11,0:10:38.38,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}我再也不会"天选"了!\N{\fnArial\fs48}I'll never choosen again!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.38,0:10:39.60,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}当然你会的\N{\fnArial\fs48}Sure you will.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.93,0:10:41.95,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}嘿,那扇门还开着\N{\fnArial\fs48}Hey, that door's still open.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.18,0:10:43.75,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}这可能是我们唯一的机会了\N{\fnArial\fs48}This might be our only chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.62,0:10:46.57,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}哦,不,别妄想了\N{\fnArial\fs48}Oh, no, you don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.02,0:10:48.09,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}放我们下来!\N{\fnArial\fs48}Put us down!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.24,0:10:50.49,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs63}你们两个麻烦大了\N{\fnArial\fs48}You two are in big trouble.
